OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1781395391
OL,3,CReform UK councillor reinstated after
OL,4,Csuspension over racist social media
OL,5,Cpost
OL,7,FReform UK have reinstated a Sunderland
OL,8,Fcouncillor to the party, after he was
OL,9,Fsuspended over racist comments he
OL,10,Freportedly posted on Facebook.
OL,12,FCllr Glenn Gibbins was one of dozens
OL,13,Fof Reform UK representatives elected
OL,14,Fto Sunderland City Council in May's
OL,15,Flocal elections.
OL,17,FIt is understood that he wrote that he
OL,18,Fcould not believe how many Nigerians
OL,19,Fthere were in the city, and that they
OL,20,Fshould be "melted down" and used to
OL,21,F"fill in pot holes".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
