PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1781395391
OL,3,CReform UK councillor reinstated after
OL,4,Csuspension over racist social media
OL,5,Cpost
OL,7,FThe now-deleted post is believed to be
OL,8,Ffrom March 2024, and was first
OL,9,Freported by the campaign group Hope
OL,10,FNot Hate.
OL,12,FAfter the comments came to light, Cllr
OL,13,FGibbins was suspended from Reform UK
OL,14,Fon Monday 11 May, just a few days
OL,15,Fafter his election.
OL,17,FBut in a statement to ITV News Tyne
OL,18,FTees on Wednesday 10 June, the party
OL,19,Fconfirmed that he has now been
OL,20,Freinstated.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
