CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1781395391
OL,3,CReform UK councillor reinstated after
OL,4,Csuspension over racist social media
OL,5,Cpost
OL,7,FA Reform spokesman said: "Following an
OL,8,Finternal disciplinary process, Cllr
OL,9,FGibbins has been readmitted to the
OL,10,Fparty and issued with a final written
OL,11,Fwarning.
OL,13,F"He has apologised for making the post
OL,14,Fand accepts that it was made in
OL,15,Fextremely poor taste showing poor
OL,16,Fjudgment."
OL,18,FCllr Gibbins represents the Hylton
OL,19,FCastle ward.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
