OL,3,CReform UK councillor reinstated after
OL,4,Csuspension over racist social media
OL,5,Cpost
OL,7,FReform UK took control of Sunderland
OL,8,FCity Council in May's election,
OL,9,Fmarking the first time that any party
OL,10,Fother than Labour has been in control
OL,11,Fof the authority since it was formed
OL,12,Fin 1974.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/4
